comments: Ayton (POR) jumps alongside Jones (WAS) and avoids making body contact as he contests the shot attempt near the rim.
Gafford (WAS) extends his arm and initiates illegal contact with Grant's (POR) head as he attempts to make the pass.
Kuzma (WAS) contests Simons' (POR) jump shot and the contact after the release, and follow-through, is marginal.
Kuzma (WAS) slightly extends his off-arm as he and Grant (POR) come together during the drive to the basket but the contact is marginal.
Ayton (POR) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Gafford (WAS) steps to his left contesting Ayton's (POR) shot attempt near the rim and the lower body contact is marginal.
Grant (POR) and Kuzma (WAS) mutually engage and disengage with one another attempting to establish position.
Grant (POR) legally contests Kuzma's (WAS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Gafford (WAS) is moving laterally when body contact occurs with Grant (POR) that affects his SQBR.

Kispert (WAS) jumps vertically and avoids initiating illegal contact with Simons (POR) during his driving shot attempt. 
 Avidja (WAS) reaches in and grazes his lower body and the contact is marginal.
Jones (WAS) passes the ball to Kuzma (WAS) and the Wizards establish frontcourt position within eight seconds.
Brogdon (POR) commits a take foul on Kuzma (WAS).
Simons (POR) initiates contact across Kuzma's (WAS) left arm, affecting his put-back shot attempt.

Replay review of the foul called on Thybulle (POR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Thybulle (POR) makes clean contact with the ball to deflect it away from Poole (WAS) and any ensuing contact is incidental.  The ball is loose at the time of the foul call and therefore, play resumes with a jump ball.
Coulibaly (WAS) moves alongside Grant's (POR) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
